channel.title: My server will not run for me or anyone else
channel.description: Hello, I have downloaded the endless pures source and the endless pures client because they both came together and I thought it would be better and easier to make it into my own so I wouldn't have to make my own client because I don't know how lol... Anyways I was wondering why I can't run it when all I did was like change the client.java and client.class where it said the old ip I think for the person that made the client and source. I changed it to my no-ip thing and now it won't even run now. I sent the client to my friend for him to check it out and he can't get it to run either. So I was just wondering how I could make it work or if someone could teach me how to make my own client somehow. Thanks for your time.[br][br][size=1]Posted on: January 24, 2009, 07:16:55 pm[/size][hr]Oh yeah another thing I need to know is like... How do you use any client with your source? Like idk nothing I do works lol...
